.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PjvD5jH4N8Hq5YhDwnWUEi.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future / Rebecca Knight)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere were so many pretty Christmas decorations on display, trust me when I say the middle aisle is in for a treat this winter. My personal favourite decoration was the playful snowman bowl and mug duo as a little decoration for the kitchen.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wDYWvNWMdbMNMFSf6DUzEi-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wDYWvNWMdbMNMFSf6DUzEi-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wDYWvNWMdbMNMFSf6DUzEi-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wDYWvNWMdbMNMFSf6DUzEi-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wDYWvNWMdbMNMFSf6DUzEi-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wDYWvNWMdbMNMFSf6DUzEi-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wDYWvNWMdbMNMFSf6DUzEi-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wDYWvNWMdbMNMFSf6DUzEi-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003c