://go.redirectingat.com/?id=92X1623319\u0026amp;xcust=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lakeland.co.uk%2F74098%2Flarge-ceramic-house-lantern-ornament-with-led-tealight\u0026amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idealhome.co.uk%2Fall-rooms%2Fall-rooms-decor%2Faldi-christmas-homeware-preview-2024\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"SkimLinks - lakeland.co.uk\" data-merchant-id=\"undefined\" data-merchant-url=\"undefined\" data-merchant-network=\"undefined\"\u003e Lakeland also has a lovely selection of LED ceramic houses for £12.99\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eI was also very impressed by the Christmas serve ware decorated with pretty little Christmas trees. Priced at £5.99, the range lands on the 14th November.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"Christmas tree white serve ware\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JFfds2h63VxTCruzuiuPEi-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://c